title: Top 30 Country Dec 23, 2014
description:
Tim McGraw retains the top position this week on the Mediabase Top 30 Country Singles chart with his latest release from Sundown Heaven Town, ?Shotgun Rider?. Brad Paisley is still in second place with ?Perfect Storm? and ?Day Drinking? by Little Big Town moves into Recurrent status. Typically there isn?t a lot of movement on the charts this time of year with many radio station music directors adding seasonal music to their playlist which results in less airtime for the other current hits.

Here are the Top 30 Country singles for the week of Dec 23, 2014 as ranked by Mediabase in 320 CBR Stereo mp3 format. 

Cheers!
